
=Bio=

"Jedediah Walls is a Media Psychologist interested in how people use media to advance themselves and society. Towards this end he acts as a social entrepreneur, and works with businesses and nonprofits on a regular basis. Commons and collaborative community projects are dear to him. He is currently working on a crowd-shared, collaborative, anyone-welcome-to-contribute book on the psychology of P2P."


